thread.title_full: Brushy Mountain Bee Farm reviewed by CHARLES BULLOCK

author: CHARLES BULLOCK
title: CHARLES BULLOCK
text: Orders arrive quickly, and accurate. With quality of wood and the price at Lowes and Home Depot I can buy hive bodies and frames cheaper than I can make them. Orders have all been accurate and advice seems correct. Will use again.
